QuestData.Title: The Warden's Signet
QuestData.Description: The night elf was carrying a signet engraved with the crest of the Wardens.$B$BThe band, made from a silvery, unbreakable metal, has been worn down by time, as if absently twisted and rubbed against its owner's finger.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Warden's Signet to Jarod Shadowsong.
